CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 3, 1961, pg. 38 reads: "Cutting Cake - Mr. and Mrs. Charles Williams cut their wedding cake at the reception which followed their recent wedding at Faith Tabernacle Church. The bride is the former Barbara Saunders. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Groom Charles Williams and bride Barbara Saunders Williams, cutting three tiered cake, with ferns and candles in background, possibly in Faith Tabernacle Church
